{"tid":1630471,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"BU 比人申請緊搜查令 (未fc，tg料)","createTime":"2019-10-06T12:37:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T13:40:49.000Z","uid":103235,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b7362a4bb1b2b1e554505efd8007256f7c3fa4e6","tid":1630471,"uid":103235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:37:11.000Z","msg":"今日有BU人比黑警拉咗，呢樣嘢絕對有可能發生，小心，清理！"},{"pid":"c5ba12d0690510fa0cf784887ac2d5542162cedf","tid":1630471,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:37:42.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"28dcab6cbb6ceb997c0e61eeefcb160aa9a015ee","tid":1630471,"uid":997,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:38:26.000Z","msg":"d野唔好放係自己間房<br />\n搵d和理非,冇出過面既人幫手"},{"pid":"c5e57d722fce5b7251a3baf3ef8e0a5fc190304d","tid":1630471,"uid":103235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:42:12.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"c73b33760183c0de524b585e27aecc477af8e94e","tid":1630471,"uid":164374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:44:09.000Z","msg":"佢地會唔會格硬拉完先再申請搜查令?"},{"pid":"8d47bcedfd14ec6bf588c9c19917c7ff22e100eb","tid":1630471,"uid":225130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:48:39.000Z","msg":"掉哂d gear就好穩陣"},{"pid":"08d0939d8de8d513d82d8c76f3a03c36db904bf7","tid":1630471,"uid":259993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:55:48.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"59d9af59ff91d07ffb8976e9cfb86f4082bfd756","tid":1630471,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:03:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"58bcfca4268a0c3f1099e001447a258a6ad9f252","tid":1630471,"uid":263367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:03:49.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"482e97e785f8721d93bcfb1b7997388d76fc0ab7","tid":1630471,"uid":73565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:04:59.000Z","msg":"唔好放房 求鳩其搵個後樓梯又好乜柒都冇<br />\n無CCTV既地方收埋<br />\n死都唔好認係自己"},{"pid":"41dca4b91d10465a79cb92ea756ef5147225fd46","tid":1630471,"uid":103235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:30:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"279c517ff49d7515234d158320228f3e54da93fc","tid":1630471,"uid":281029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7362a4bb1b2b1e554505efd8007256f7c3fa4e6","tid":1630471,"uid":103235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:37:11.000Z","msg":"今日有BU人比黑警拉咗，呢樣嘢絕對有可能發生，小心，清理！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:40:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">傳黑警正向法庭申請搜查令，浸大宿舍宿生快啲執埋啲嘢走<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TQ8njEZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTQ8njEZ.jpg&h=39a4de91&s={SIZE}\" /></span>"}]}